title: Indiabulls Housing Finance Q3 Results: Net profit down 8% to Rs 303 cr - Economic Times
content: Indiabulls Housing Finance Q3 Results: Net profit down 8% to Rs 303 cr  Economic Times
description: In Q3 FY22, the company disbursed retail loans of around Rs 2,800 crore. It disbursed Rs 1,573 crore through co-lending tie-ups with seven institutions.
